Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.24,0:02:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子好饿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.30,0:02:27.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,CM 明天也…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.66,0:02:29.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天也会去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.79,0:02:31.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.77,0:02:33.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也差不多这时候回来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.40,0:02:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.97,0:02:38.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 克里斯酱也去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.34,0:02:41.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不太喜欢人多的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.46,0:02:43.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得第二天应该不会有那么多人了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.99,0:02:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 冈伦也一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.75,0:02:54.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冈部 出来一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.85,0:02:59.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.12,0:03:01.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来后就一直闷闷不乐的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.50,0:03:04.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道真由理是担心你才跟你搭话的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.16,0:03:06.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.80,0:03:09.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我怎能保持冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.87,0:03:11.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是明天了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.88,0:03:16.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算今天没事 等到明天…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.69,0:03:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这已经是第几次对你这样了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.00,0:03:24.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.50,0:03:26.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冈部?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.22,0:03:31.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有事想告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.81,0:03:37.82,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(700,652)}无限连锁的细胞凋亡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.43,0:03:43.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由理她…明天就…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.94,0:03:46.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕会死
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.26,0:03:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一开始是13日的晚上死
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.10,0:03:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随着每一封D-MAIL的撤销
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.69,0:03:55.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死期就推迟一天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.05,0:04:00.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明天会跟着她一起去CM
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.88,0:04:02.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有救她的办法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.84,0:04:07.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想送她最后一程
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.56,0:04:08.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.33,0:04:12.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想弄清楚这条世界线上她确切的死亡时间
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.40,0:04:16.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此之上再进行一次时间跳跃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.94,0:04:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有别的办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.11,0:04:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来要撤销的是那个叫作桐生萌郁的邮件吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.90,0:04:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 内容我也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.02,0:04:35.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是让过去的自己不要换手机型号
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.29,0:04:39.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次必须用那家伙的手机发送才行…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.27,0:04:41.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去找她
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.31,0:04:47.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟真由理去CM
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.49,0:04:48.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.54,0:04:50.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果顺利的话 在真由理…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.60,0:04:53.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在她变成那样之前也许会有什么办法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.66,0:04:54.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明白吗?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.21,0:04:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我找不到萌郁的话 那就…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.61,0:04:58.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会马上联络你的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.44,0:05:04.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 不管什么事都可以告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.04,0:05:08.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论什么事 无论什么时候都来找我商量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.94,0:05:12.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 至今为止你都…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.95,0:05:18.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要忘记 无论你身处哪条世界线
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.98,0:05:21.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你都不是一个人 还有我在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.34,0:05:32.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在在有明
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.92,0:05:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里聚集了好多人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.41,0:05:35.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在超乎预料
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.96,0:05:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.67,0:05:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然萌郁没有回信 但是已经找到了她打工的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.47,0:05:47.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去那里调查一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.61,0:05:50.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解 不要乱来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.70,0:05:55.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桐生…萌郁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.14,0:05:59.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前只做了两三天就辞了的那个好像是叫这个名字
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.99,0:06:00.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住所?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.13,0:06:03.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道是知道 但你是谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.80,0:06:20.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.87,0:06:21.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.85,0:06:27.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桐生萌郁她…自杀了?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.92,0:06:29.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有搞错吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.76,0:06:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.02,0:06:32.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天夜里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.23,0:06:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遗体已经转移到了千代田第三医院
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.10,0:06:36.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她好像举目无亲的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.35,0:06:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也在等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.58,0:06:37.81,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.83,0:06:44.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.40,0:06:45.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自杀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.82,0:06:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.58,0:06:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是被同伴杀了?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.97,0:06:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在杀死真由理之前…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.58,0:06:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.13,0:07:01.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理由什么的无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.19,0:07:04.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去 真由理就…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.15,0:07:08.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间跳跃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.41,0:07:10.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间跳跃到萌郁死亡之前
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.82,0:07:30.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.08,0:07:39.50,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冈…冈部… 真…真由理…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.70,0:07:39.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死亡时间是19点52分
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.64,0:07:42.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.39,0:07:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 冈部 你把这个吃了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.15,0:07:52.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.61,0:07:54.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是清清楚楚的写着「牧瀬」吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.86,0:07:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你在听吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.78,0:08:00.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要忘记 你不是一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.24,0:08:05.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 的确是啊 红莉栖
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.33,0:08:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…刚刚说了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.75,0:08:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认识一个叫桐生萌郁的女人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.25,0:08:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎? 那是谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.21,0:08:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是时间跳跃回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.71,0:08:18.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.38,0:09:03.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,FB…FB…FB…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.01,0:09:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我…求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.47,0:09:12.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,FB 为什么 为什么不回邮件啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.39,0:09:18.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了 回复我啊 FB
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.73,0:09:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桐生萌郁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.44,0:09:25.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都按照吩咐行事 为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.07,0:09:26.28,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我啊 冈部
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.49,0:09:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请回复邮件啊 FB
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.08,0:09:30.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你听不到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.41,0:09:31.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.04,0:09:40.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,FB FB FB FB FB
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.88,0:09:45.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.78,0:10:05.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.86,0:10:08.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝对不原谅这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.75,0:10:18.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.88,0:10:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.09,0:10:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.84,0:10:27.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.01,0:10:29.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是牧瀬 手机怎么样了?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.47,0:10:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抢过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.51,0:10:31.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,D-MAIL的设定就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.89,0:10:32.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经设定好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.22,0:10:34.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说什么声音啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.43,0:10:36.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用在意 真由理呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.73,0:10:37.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在显像管工房
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.90,0:10:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,42寸电视机也开着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.86,0:10:40.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.90,0:10:44.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红莉栖 启动吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.74,0:10:45.62,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\fs95\be2\frz-28\an1\pos(67,458)}想换的那个型号已\N经很快卖光了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.07,0:10:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.49,0:10:52.41,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还给我 还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.99,0:10:51.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是最后一封了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.83,0:10:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要发送了这个 真由理就…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.85,0:11:15.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还给我 还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.14,0:11:16.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把手机还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.73,0:11:18.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事 什么都没发生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.14,0:11:20.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.10,0:11:20.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你发送了?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.02,0:11:23.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发送了 启动没问题吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.15,0:11:24.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放电现象出现了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.65,0:11:25.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.57,0:11:27.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Reading steiner没有发动!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.20,0:11:33.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Reading steiner没有发动 这是为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.37,0:11:41.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还给我 还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.21,0:11:41.50,*Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.88,0:11:46.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还给我 还给我 还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.21,0:11:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.67,0:11:52.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,D-MAIL根据接收对象的不同效果也不同
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.68,0:11:56.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说你写的内容还不足以改变桐生萌郁的行动?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.89,0:11:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那到底该怎么做…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.48,0:12:07.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有变
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.19,0:12:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙根本没换过手机啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.99,0:12:12.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.07,0:12:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是确认过的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.99,0:12:17.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4天前 我换了手机
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.49,0:12:20.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想告诉自己 还是不要换比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.83,0:12:23.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发送前一刻 她写了别的内容啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.79,0:12:24.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.84,0:12:26.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说你不知道D-MAIL的内容吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.92,0:12:28.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收件箱里应该还留着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.38,0:12:30.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在就调查看看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.84,0:12:36.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还给我 还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.22,0:12:38.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 冈部
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.68,0:12:39.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冈部?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.52,0:12:41.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再打给你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.77,0:12:46.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还给我 还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.36,0:12:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还给我 还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.53,0:12:59.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 你们在搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.95,0:13:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还给我 冈部
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.97,0:13:14.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还给我 还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.98,0:13:30.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 到底在搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.49,0:13:37.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.04,0:13:47.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 最近的情侣真是的 喔好可怕好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.77,0:14:13.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样 怎么样你才肯还给我?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.53,0:14:17.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还记得你发送过D-MAIL的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.74,0:14:20.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,D…什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.12,0:14:24.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个星期前 你应该收到过一封奇怪的短信
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.79,0:14:26.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从未来的自己那里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.83,0:14:29.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.17,0:14:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我内容 然后我就还给你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.34,0:14:35.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 不能说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.43,0:14:41.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是跟IBN5100 还有Rounders有关的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.60,0:14:42.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说中了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.85,0:14:45.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我 邮件的内容是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.02,0:14:49.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想我还你手机了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.02,0:14:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能背叛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.90,0:14:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背叛谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.82,0:14:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那个叫FB的家伙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.19,0:15:00.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的指示都是FB下达的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.66,0:15:03.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,FB就是我的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.20,0:15:06.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙就是你们的指挥官吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.79,0:15:11.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能背叛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.67,0:15:13.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是忠心耿耿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.67,0:15:18.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊 那个叫FB的家伙好像根本不在乎你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.76,0:15:22.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你将被那家伙抛弃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.97,0:15:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没…这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.39,0:15:26.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他没有联络你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.27,0:15:30.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他背叛了你 抛弃了你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.15,0:15:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.15,0:15:33.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,FB不是那种人!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.16,0:15:45.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,FB…拯救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.79,0:15:49.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只是被利用了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.36,0:16:14.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs45}招募Rounders
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.64,0:16:14.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道我为什么能如此断言么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.57,0:16:19.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,FB就像妈妈一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.19,0:16:20.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是怎样的工作?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.91,0:16:26.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\fs95\be2\pos(1003,171)}提问
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.91,0:16:26.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\fs95\be2\an4\pos(0,530)}当然。会提供和本人\N相衬的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.57,0:16:24.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拥有真正的时间机器
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.49,0:16:26.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从未来发来的邮件就是证据
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.54,0:16:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也能胜任吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.34,0:16:32.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\fs95\be2\pos(1123,201)}继续提问
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.34,0:16:32.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\fs95\be2\pos(239,371)}是的 不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.29,0:16:32.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说了需要我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.75,0:16:36.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有工作经验 也没有任何特长
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.59,0:16:41.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fs45}没关系 一起加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.10,0:16:51.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我亲眼目睹了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.64,0:16:52.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.02,0:16:55.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.28,0:17:02.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4天后 你将在这房间里自杀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.57,0:17:07.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直等待着FB的联络
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.37,0:17:09.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人在这里孤零零地死去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.08,0:17:10.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.79,0:17:11.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.33,0:17:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,FB已经不会再联络你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.29,0:17:17.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你被抛弃了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.84,0:17:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.84,0:17:21.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是从什么时候开始没有收到回复的? 啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.76,0:17:23.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直在等待吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.59,0:17:25.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不觉得奇怪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.43,0:17:30.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会在这里死去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.22,0:17:32.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.02,0:17:33.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这个昏暗而空荡的房间里!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.27,0:17:35.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.06,0:17:36.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀了真由理的你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.77,0:17:39.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里 孤零零地 被人抛弃背叛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.65,0:17:40.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就如同垃圾一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.90,0:17:43.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结束掉生命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.74,0:17:42.57,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.45,0:17:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁也不会来救你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.49,0:17:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,FB也不会!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.07,0:17:52.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.54,0:17:57.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.82,0:18:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.91,0:18:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说她像母亲一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.58,0:18:37.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,FB是女人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.13,0:18:40.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.63,0:18:41.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.30,0:18:44.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没见过她
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.63,0:18:46.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不想见她
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.18,0:18:51.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见面的话肯定会让她失望的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.27,0:18:55.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说 估计连电话也没打过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.27,0:18:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真亏你会对那家伙唯命是从
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.56,0:19:01.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她给了我容身之所
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.57,0:19:02.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,容身之所?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.28,0:19:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真是傻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.63,0:19:17.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\fs200\be6\frz-16\pos(360,447)}老式PC在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.63,0:19:18.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\fs200\be6\pos(967,549)}{\frx20}{\frz32}柳林神社仓库
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.17,0:19:19.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frx30\frz-5\bord0\fs200\be6\pos(777,244)}立刻回收
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.04,0:19:21.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冈部
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.63,0:19:26.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别害我担心啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.21,0:19:28.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为我…担心了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.01,0:19:30.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没担心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.68,0:19:31.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.43,0:19:33.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.22,0:19:38.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那偷走IBN5100的就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.56,0:19:39.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是萌郁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.81,0:19:41.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那现在在哪?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.81,0:19:43.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再多问了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.61,0:19:46.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按原计划撤销D-MAIL
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.82,0:19:49.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是7月31日 上午11点左右吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.79,0:20:00.26,Default_tip,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别去神社 这是陷阱 东西不在那边
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.29,0:20:00.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,启动了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.00,0:20:04.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次一定要…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.31,0:20:19.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.48,0:20:20.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.52,0:20:21.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.90,0:20:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过去的桐生萌郁没有相信这条D-MAIL吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.73,0:20:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了以防万一 她还是按照第一条D-MAIL说的去做了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.86,0:20:32.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用别的内容再试一次…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.87,0:20:34.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.45,0:20:37.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕能让萌郁行动的只有那个家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.95,0:20:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能用那家伙的手机发邮件的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.37,0:20:42.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萌郁应该会无条件服从
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.50,0:20:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙是指?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.43,0:20:54.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要找到FB
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.47,0:20:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道她可能在哪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.60,0:21:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算有也不会说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.27,0:21:03.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚才说的 我杀了人…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.40,0:21:05.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是未来的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.77,0:21:09.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 如果是FB的命令 你会干的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.32,0:21:12.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会干 一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.70,0:21:14.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算知道自己只是被利用了?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.66,0:21:19.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你像这样一直依赖她
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.74,0:21:21.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被抛弃后只能去死!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.12,0:21:24.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4天后 8月15日
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.04,0:21:27.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的死亡已经被这个世界决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.09,0:21:29.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你无法反抗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.17,0:21:33.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我却要反抗!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.01,0:21:35.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要跟这个世界抗争到底
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.18,0:21:40.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要救出真由理!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.41,0:21:56.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投币储物箱
